<div id="header">
<h1>Chunkify</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p><a href="#">Chunkify</a> is an analysis pass for the <a href="RSSA">RSSA</a>
<a href="IntermediateLanguage">IntermediateLanguage</a>, invoked from <a href="ToMachine">ToMachine</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_description">Description</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>It partitions all the labels (function and block) in an <a href="RSSA">RSSA</a>
program into disjoint sets, referred to as chunks.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_implementation">Implementation</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/MLton/mlton/blob/master/mlton/backend/chunkify.sig"><code>chunkify.sig</code></a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><a href="https://github.com/MLton/mlton/blob/master/mlton/backend/chunkify.fun"><code>chunkify.fun</code></a></p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_details_and_notes">Details and Notes</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Breaking large <a href="RSSA">RSSA</a> functions into chunks is necessary for
reasonable compile times with the <a href="CCodegen">CCodegen</a> and the <a href="LLVMCodegen">LLVMCodegen</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
